        <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 leading-relaxed mb-4 line-clamp-2">Master Korean vocabulary with spaced repetition. Learn Hangul, common words, and study techniques for K-pop, K-drama, and TOPIK.</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-ink-400 font-semibold">8 min read</span>
      </a>

      <!-- Spanish -->
      <a href="/blog/learn-spanish-vocabulary-with-flashcards/" class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-parchment-200 p-6 hover:border-gold-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 reveal-up delay-1">
