        <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 leading-relaxed mb-4 line-clamp-2">Build Spanish vocabulary fast with flashcards. From beginner to fluent, learn the most effective techniques for memorizing Spanish words.</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-ink-400 font-semibold">8 min read</span>
      </a>

      <!-- Tips -->
      <a href="/blog/how-to-stay-consistent-with-language-learning/" class="group bg-white rounded-xl border border-parchment-200 p-6 hover:border-gold-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 reveal-up delay-2">
        <span class="inline-block bg-gold-50 text-gold-700 px-3 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold mb-4 border border-gold-100">Tips</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-base font-bold text-ink-800 mb-2 leading-snug group-hover:text-gold-600 transition-colors">How to Stay Consistent with Language Learning</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-500 leading-relaxed mb-4 line-clamp-2">Build a daily study habit that sticks. Practical strategies for staying motivated with flashcards and spaced repetition.</p>
        <span class="text-xs text-ink-400 font-semibold">7 min read</span>
      </a>

